'''''Kathakku Pinnil''''' is a [[Malayalam films of 1987|1987]] [[Cinema of India|Indian]] [[Malayalam language|Malayalam]] film, directed by [[KG George]] and produced by Mathew Paulose. The film stars [[Mammootty]], Devi Lalitha, [[Lalu Alex]] and [[Jagathy Sreekumar]] in lead roles. The film had musical score by [[Ouseppachan]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.malayalachalachithram.com/movie.php?i=2039|title=Kadhaykku Pinnil|accessdate=2014-10-17|publisher=www.malayalachalachithram.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://malayalasangeetham.info/m.php?4943|title=Kadhaykku Pinnil|accessdate=2014-10-17|publisher=malayalasangeetham.info}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://spicyonion.com/title/kathakku-pinnil-malayalam-movie/|title=Kathakku Pinnil|accessdate=2014-10-17|publisher=spicyonion.com}}</ref>

